I've marked the Haskell resits - the scripts are in the SGO.  The main 
purpose of the exercise is to prepare you better for the exam on Friday 
- don't worry about the mark too much, although the nominal pass mark is 
15/30.  Some of you handed in solutions that were not unique.  Where 
